8 An Act relating to counties; amending 19 O.S. 2021,
Section 8.2, which relates to the authority to adopt
9 or amend county home rule charter; providing for
increasing population threshold for adopting or
10 amending county home rule charter; updating statutory
language; and providing an effective date.
11
12
13 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
14 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 19 O.S. 2021, Section 8.2, is
15 amended to read as follows:
16 Section 8.2. Any county in this state with a population of less
17 than five hundred fifty thousand (550,000) eight hundred seventy-
18 five thousand (875,000), according to the latest Federal Decennial
19 Census, which contains a metropolitan area municipality with a
20 population of two hundred fifty thousand (250,000) seven hundred
21 thousand (700,000) or more, according to the latest Federal
22 Decennial Census, may adopt or amend a County Home Rule Charter for
23 county government which specifies those powers appropriate for said
24
